kgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28771483df060a93919acb5c9b74105ecd5ab988","tid":1327111,"uid":225916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:06:20.000Z","msg":"帶油<br />\n帶雞蛋<br />\n帶噴漆呀"},{"pid":"fb3086a5ab025842a6d484ae2955ad785924a53b","tid":1327111,"uid":92348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"加野喇!!!!<br />\n第六項訴求：撒回智能燈柱計劃<br />\n第七項訴求：撒回社會信用系統計劃<br />\n第八項訴求：撒回政府設施架裝容貌識別系統"},{"pid":"b41e33f44df782450278cef06de52b0d4b7dc0d7","tid":1327111,"uid":73565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:19:38.000Z","msg":"獨立調查不如變警隊改革"},{"pid":"535d81a92eb54e6c3a9b34ef8ff0a431a3df0249","tid":1327111,"uid":269683,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:19:44.000Z","msg":"其實地形有無得再諗 完左遊行再去第二度集會？"},{"pid":"d598f85bcc85166d02922200d3bc5b0453bf096f","tid":1327111,"uid":131122,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:22:29.000Z","msg":"唯獨不認同增加訴求<br />\n根本有雙普選就一百大訴求都有機會做"},{"pid":"b00361b53198b029cec2ac1c7ee75c57b4bf4e35","tid":1327111,"uid":83063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:25:00.000Z","msg":"我想講少少野   大家可唔可以唔好再聽果D所謂義工講既野？<br />\n唔係要割蓆   但佢地剩係識叫我地退  <br />\n上次發夢係源禾路我見住隻狗用爪扯走人地個口罩  然後俾CAM 影佢全貌  仲整到臉上有血痕  D 社工都剩係識叫人退退退 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"966136b0c8b9f6fd7d897ba07b6f712faf18f20a","tid":1327111,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"36df9257f5705ae99ca472203a8e6ba16d3cc6b0","tid":1327111,"uid":124932,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:29:49.000Z","msg":"防守平價工具<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47bsPp2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47bsPp2.png&h=cda54be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uuYrkwL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuuYrkwL.png&h=255fa3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察可以係防線灑呢啲釘同波子，由於警察極少主動推進，主要係暴徒主動攻擊警方防線，所以警察只要守好，等暴徒沖過來過左防線還拖就得<br />\n<br />\n情況一：對峙<br />\n暴徒唔郁，掟啲釘過去暴徒度，當暴徒要行動果陣要留意地下，移速攻速低，警察可以呢個時候還拖<br />\n<br />\n情況二：防守<br />\n求其灑係鐵馬防線度，暴徒沖過來一個唔覺意就會中伏<br />\n<br />\n情況三：撤退<br />\n邊退邊灑，佢想襲警都追唔到你<br />\n<br />\n主要作用<br />\n1. 鞋薄，吉腳<br />\n2. 鞋厚，吉入去，釘個頂痴係鞋底，會跣<br />\n3. 吉唔入但踩中波子，趴落釘度<br />\n4. 好小心乜事都冇，但攻速移速大減<br />\n<br />\n希望警察可以盡快擊敗敵人"},{"pid":"e167ee49547fbaf1a73aec931e4f6fa3925fff9d","tid":1327111,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T13:45:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cbebbbdff519601c391651a8dbf287211133cff","tid":1327111,"uid":68822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T14:21:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DkVURRBwauKE&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQskPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=9e486af2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kVURRBwauKE</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-nY--PG-tFM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-nY--PG-tFM&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQskPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=1589338c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-nY--PG-tFM</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n[反送中]【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n沒有暴民，只有暴政<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山　各自努力<br />\n不割蓆　不篤灰　不分化　不捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n七大訴求<br />\n　- 全面落實雙真普選<br />\n　- 永久完全撤回逃犯條<br />\n　- 釋放所有反送中被捕抗爭示威者<br />\n　- 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n　- 撤回暴動定性<br />\n　- 永不實行社會信用評分系統<br />\n　- 收回多功能智慧監控燈柱<br />\n<br />\n<em>&lsquo;It's not about how much we lost, it's about how much we have left.&rsquo;<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> (Avengers: Endgame)</span></em><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F8Nr2YF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF8Nr2YF.jpg&h=93a6d743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721! HONGKONGERS! ASSEMBLE!</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"48ce637695e2d8e5d91d57915fadcea111e37664","tid":1327111,"uid":41181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"3d6f0cfa949c8aa192f025da88cdfeed9c7e71ac","tid":1327111,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:43:09.000Z","msg":"發夢試下不要去金鐘，去西環，出其不意。"},{"pid":"61979f4c9b605c6e8830bf329264d6355fce0e5b","tid":1327111,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T15:45:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sFgUwbzqsMw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsFgUwbzqsMw&d=yxFCeCsiIqqjoL8q9QcQskPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=f9532e0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sFgUwbzqsMw</a><br />\n老徐，干非對談。"},{"pid":"094f21ac31c4c17c60c5778f8e4e4eba6ff5cc67","tid":1327111,"uid":199727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T19:15:20.000Z","msg":"721見"}]}